column2: Breezy- misty- more activity than usual.
Assumed time was 12:00.  Lake level: Rising
Assumed time was 12:00.  Lake level: Rising
Ice off- like a mirror- so still.  Pollen dust present.
Calm- but lake stirred up by storm on 6/10
Clear- floating cotton wood fuzz- calm- much rain
Sunny- very still water- quiet activity over weekend
Lake still as glass- lots of floating debris from a strong wind the day before.
Sunny- hot- humid and very still
If weather improves will record more before winter.
Bright- clear- sunny- light breeze- some pollen on surface.
Hot humid- mild- breezy- sunny.  Lots of cottonwood pollen + the farmers were aerial spraying.
Gray and gloomy- hot and humid- just a bare breeze.  A few fishermen- many small fish by the shore.  Water lilies scout this year- two or three white and the balance yellow
Did my reading in 19' of water.
Calm- mild- some pollen on water at shore.  Will try to do one more in October
Partly sunny- light breeze (se) - very light rain on May 23- very windy over the weekend- no boat traffic.
Some algae- some cotton wood- much pollen- hot- humid- partly sunny.
Scant algae.  Lots of cottonwood.  Gorgeous day.
Hot humid sunny calm.  A few dead fish.
Hot- humid- sunny and calm- lots of cottonwood.
Sunny + warm with light breeze.  For this lake lots of activity: 8 pontoons- swimmers- some low power boats.
Sunny warm with light breeze.  Water looks very clear but is a tea color.  Same at fish lake.
Partly sunny- still mild.  So nice I did some drifting and dreaming.  Excellent fishing.
Gray- gloomy- hot humid- light breeze.
Gray- gloomy- mild humid- light breeze.
Clouds breaking up- hot- humid- light breeze.  Rained 1-5 a.m.
Cloudy- lots of rain over weekend.
Gorgeous day.  Tested in 18' of water.  Water level Up a bit
Partly sunny pleasant breezy.  In 17' of water.  Water level: unchanged.
Couldn't use depth finder today.  By secchi disk.  I was in 15' of water.
Beautiful day.  Lake like a mirror.
Water level: Up a bit w/ the 3" of rain
Ice off 3 weeks ago- clear- calm and mild.
Overcast- beginning to sprinkle- mild- calm like a mirror.  Water level: unchanged.
Sunny- cool + calm.  Lake like a mirror.  Pollen on surface.  Water level: unchanged.
Sun out now. calm- not a breath of air. lots of tree pollen.  Water level: unchanged.
Bright- clear- sunny- cool. lake like a mirror. surface of entire lake covered with bug bodies.
At a depth of 12' saw a snapping turtle resting at the bottom. tested in 19' water. finally a really nice day.
Perfect day- some green scum on the N shore.
Partly sunny light breeze. lovely day. water warm.
Sunny mild light breeze. lots of small fish close to shore.
Bright clear sunny mild. drifting and dreaming.
A lovely turnover to canoe.  Water level: unchanged.
Bright sunny mild + calm.  Water level: unchanged.
Glorious day- calm + mild. barely cloudy water.  Water level: unchanged.
Partly sunny- cool- calm. lake down about 2". water so clear.
A gorgeous fall day with a slight breeze.  Water is clear with a few weeds at the top near shore.
A gorgeous fall day. water clear as a bell.
Water level: UP A LITTLE. 6" OF RAIN
Water level: UP A LITTLE. 6" OF RAIN
Water level: UP- DUE TO SIX INCHES OF RAIN
Bright + sunny- 10-12 mph wind.  1 boat on lake.  2 loons on lake/heron/crane(2).
Mostly sunny- 5-8 mph wind- 1 boat on lake.  Quiet and peaceful.
Sunny- mid 80s.  Very light wind.  2 boats.
Sunny- 8-10 mph wind.  No boats.  Saw an egret this morning.
